Dear Mr. Ney,<br><br>
Although I am a Professor in the Department of Nutrition at UC Davis, I also trained in geography (cultural; emphasis on Africa and the Middle East).<br><br>
Please check out our class web-site for materials that you can inspect and log-down. <br><br>
http://www-honors.ucdavis.edu/html/vietnam/vntp.html<br><br>
